    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_2514506226483487424.png",
                "id": "talent78827",
                "key": "Sword of the Radiant Path",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Sword of the Radiant Path"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span><br>Creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Curtain of Slumber Shield</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shooting Star</span>. <br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Curtain of Slumber Shield</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br>Provides <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">2 Shield points </span>to defend your active character.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shooting Star</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your character uses a Skill:</span> Accumulate 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Star</span>. If you have at least 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Stars</span>, consume 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Stars</span> and deal 1 <span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">Cryo DMG</span>. (The Skill that causes this Combat Status will also trigger this effect)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When causing this Combat Status again:</span> Accumulate 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Stars</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/de48c78ad3dc782b2dfe98bbe645f7cd_8385278481278670118.png",
                "id": "talent9887",
                "key": "Nights of Formal Focus",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Nights of Formal Focus"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span><br>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Celestial Dreamsphere</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/1af1d6edbe77aedd11a2e57551afb598_5350779496507280059.png",
                "id": "talent99487",
                "key": "Dream of the Star-Stream Shaker",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dream of the Star-Stream Shaker"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>. If <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Shooting Star</span> is in play, it will gain 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Star</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Shooting Star</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After your character uses a Skill:</span> Accumulate 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Star</span>. If you have at least 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Stars</span>, consume 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Stars</span> and deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>. (The Skill that causes this Combat Status will also trigger this effect)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When causing this Combat Status again:</span> Accumulate 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Night Stars</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1096313429085297390.png",
                "id": "talent30281",
                "key": "Celestial Dreamsphere",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/8fae1317e614df75bd7911789c244c1f_9187685471906236424.png",
                "title": "Celestial Dreamsphere"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Cryo and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives Physical or Pyro DMG, in which case they will take +2 DMG)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_7358130837517779181.png",
                "id": "talent12094",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Shield</span></strong></p><p>This Shield will be consumed to protect the character who equips it from DMG.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3303906377069633155.png",
